'''''Face of Nepal''''' is [[Asia|Asia’s]] largest model hunt platform where Nepalese models participate to be offered the chance to represent Nepal at the Asia New Star Model Contest.
== The Competition == Face of Nepal was started in 2016 by Badal Saboo,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.faceofnepal.co/|title=Face of Nepal.co|last=|first=|date=|website=Face of Nepal.co|publisher=|access-date=21 May 2016}}</ref> with the prize for the 4 top winners going to [[Suwon|Suwon City, Korea]] to compete in the Asia New Model Contest,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://en.amfa.or.kr/newstar-about?ckattempt=1|title=Introduction to 2016 Asia New Star Model Contest|last=|first=|date=|website=Asia Model Festival in Suwon|publisher=|access-date=21 May 2016}}</ref> a contest partnered with the Korea Model Association (KMA).<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://glamournepal.net/four-nepalese-represent-asia-new-star-model-contest-2016/|title=Four Nepalese to represent at Asia New Star Model contest 2016|last=|first=|date=19 April 2016|website=Glamour Nepal|publisher=|access-date=21 May 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.models-np.com/about-contest?ck|title=2016 Face of Nepal|last=|first=|date=|website=Face of Nepal|publisher=|access-date=21 May 2016}}</ref> The KMA has organized the Asia Model Festival, Asia's largest, for the past 10 years.
The Face of Nepal 2016 pageant took place on April 29, 2016 at [[Kathmandu]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://kathmandupost.ekantipur.com/printedition/news/2016-04-17/nepal-in-the-race-of-asia-new-star-model-contest.html|title=Nepal in the race of Asia New Star Model Contest|last=|first=|date=17 April 2016|website=The Kathmandu Post|publisher=|access-date=21 May 2016}}</ref> The winners were [[Ritesh Raj Gurung]] and [[Al Hang Rae]], who won the prize. First runner up went to [[Parmita RL Rana]] and [[Sameer Kunwar Rana]] who withdrew due to personal reasons, resulting in [[Bhaskar Baniya]] being given the 1st runner up title. The Asia New Model Contest took place on the 19th of May 2016, with 25 countries taking place.
